content: Hello! I‚Äôve signed up for a number of phone banks and attended part one of the Online Engagement Training this afternoon. Are there any opportunities available to get more involved with the campaign efforts here in Delaware or nearby PA? I work in marketing (focus on brand and content marketing) and am a former reporter, but I‚Äôm happy to help with whatever is needed on the ground
I haven't  seen any in DE but there may be in PA since it's a battle ground. I apologize,  I'm struggling  to keep  up with  all the messages  and trainings, I wish I could help you more.
You know in Reach  there are opportunities  in every county through the Democrats Offices  in every county and some online phone and text banking  in other states. Do you have Reach?

<@1269333062097961060>  I found something  for you ... look in Reach in Democrats  Campaigne,  you'll if on your profile  you add Delaware,  PA, and National  you'll get these events in " Events" on Reach. Amy
<@1261723980910563331>  thank you Amy! Yes, I've started using Reach to sign up for events in PA. Much appreciated!
You're welcome.

This is just a reminder that you can sign up to phone bank, canvass, get trainings  or take other actions at https://events.democrats.org/ in your state or in one of our battleground states (NC, PA, GA, NH, WI, PA, MI, AZ, NV). Volunteers like you make all the difference! We look forward to seeing you at an event soon.
